fields.value: CAPS Administrative Units and Bonus split (CAPS-ADMINQ CAPS-BIGBON CAPS-BSPLIT CAPS-MISCQ modules)

dsDescriptionValue.value:
These administrative units ask Rs to evaluate aspects of the CAPS project itself. It includes several measures of how well Rs feel that they have gotten to know their team members, whether they prefer working alone or with others, feelings about the computer and computer communication, evaluations of CAPS units, suggestions for improving the project, and other comments. It also gives Rs an opportunity to give open-ended responses to a question about how they would like to see the $1000 end-of -year bonus divided.

These units present Rs with various options for dividing and awarding an end-of-year bonus. R's choices are recorded. Units vary from year to year. Source code is self-documenting.

In CAPS/88 end of year bonus questions are in ADMINQ1-6, in CAPS/87 they are in ADMINQ and BIGBON1-3, in CAPS/86 they are in BSPLIT1-3, in CAPS/85 they are in MISCQ1-4, in CAPS/84 they are in ADMINQ1-10.

Several of these units also contain info about attitudes toward other CAPS m embers, grades, the computer.

No standard scoring.
